                    Get a fully personalized experience with this feature and motivate yourself on executing 
                    actions you really enjoy and want to do.</p>
                </div>
                <img class="col-lg-6 p-0" src="{{ asset('assets/image/home_new_quest.PNG') }}" />
            </div>

            <div class="row mt-5">
                <img class="col-lg-6  p-0" src="{{ asset('assets/image/home_valid_quest.PNG') }}" />
                <div class="col-lg-6 mt-5 text-center my-auto">
                    <h3>Go at your own pace</h3>
                    <p>With the quests validation system, you can validate your quests whenever you want. 
                    Don't get in your own way while wanting to do everything at the same time, 
                    you aren't limited in your quests and can do as many as you want and as frequently as you want.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

